::KitKat3::
She walked down the hall and found Drillbit, Killfest and Starscream 
there. She stood there with a stunned look on her face. "You, your 
all alive? By the matrix, I don't know how, but your alive!"  She ran 
up and put her arms around Drillbit. "I missed you. I thought you 
were dead or something."  She kissed him without hesitation. 
Then she heard the alarms and looked at the others. "What's going on?"
She looked at Starscream and Killfest.  "Who's in charge since I 
left?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

::KitKat2::
She sat down at the entrance to the Allience base.  She didn't know 
where she was, but she could smell her own scent all around. "I don't 
remember being here," she said to herself. "Perhaps this was where 
DarkMouse fixed me up at."  She scratched at the door. "Hey, jokes 
over, you can let me in now. Drillbit? DarkMouse? GoldenEye? 
Starscream? Killfest? OK, this isn't funny anymore.  I know you have 
a holoprojector on the front door now. Come on guys, play time's 
over. Let me in." She sat back down and waited for someone to let her 
in.
